cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.HC. 

The paper presents a dataset of articulated objects and human interactions with them, which is relevant to robotics (cs.RO) and computer vision (cs.CV) research. The dataset includes annotations of object poses and kinematic states, which could be useful for machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) applications. Additionally, the recorded human interactions could be relevant to human-computer interaction (cs.HC) research.
